Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.88,0:00:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before they came here, they were really alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when they were found near \N the border of Czechoslovakia...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I heard they were walking together, hand in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both shivering from the cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.93,0:00:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the orphanage in East Germany \N were horrible at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't compare us to Kinderheim 511
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inge, that is not the way to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.05,0:00:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.  It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to be scared of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:00:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, you can go to the bathroom by yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.65,0:01:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These children don't know the love of their true parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need love in order to mature as a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.99,0:01:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you said, the orphanages in East Germany at the time were terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place used to be called Orphanage No. 47, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, we still tried our best \N to make something happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tried to go against the government, even slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we wouldn't turn out to be like Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That place was a special orphanage \N under the cooperative jurisdiction...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the Ministry of Health and Welfare \N and the Ministry of Domestic Affairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.43,0:01:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the internal conditions were monitored by the Ministry of Domestic Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that place was old East Germany's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...testing facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A testing facility?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:35.82,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,163)\pos(356,310)}A Little Experiment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a project to turn children into perfect soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Psychological conditioning...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Research into brainwashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They formed conspiracies among the orphans...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and monitored how they hated and fought \N each other under those circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:04:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An experiment for creating a cold-hearted \N person, one without sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you imagine what kind of people those children \N would turn out to be when they grew up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now we don't have any proof \N of what went on in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because it appears everything related to that matter was burned right before the wall came down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones in the Ministry of Domestic Affairs who \N were involved in the project fled as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have heard one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was one person...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who successfully hid his personal \N history and settled in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A supervisor for Kinderheim 511's demonic project.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His true identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was that of a child psychologist who worked for \N the ministry of Domestic Affair's police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though on the outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he said he used to work for the Ministry of Health \N and Welfare and was in charge of this district.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worked for the Ministry of Health and Welfare...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and was in charge of this district...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done, Inge?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every thing is in the dark now, thanks to that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That... incident...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened at Kinderheim 511?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I said too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dredged up something I didn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me what happened at that place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is my soccer ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is my soccer ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, it is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, it is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't play soccer until you are all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man said he will be coming to pick you up soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so sleep well until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I don't know what really happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because at the time, the government of East Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...issued a gag order regarding the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, it was the unnatural death \N of the director of Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a dispute broke out amongst the instructors \N over who would succeed the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard anarchy ensured inside the orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was impossible to control the conspiracies \N of the children in that situation, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised Johan was able to get out of there alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what happened to Kinderheim 511?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every member of the orphanage, \N including the instructors...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...killed each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the world is in an abyss is the biggest lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow will definitely be a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone is here to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hartmann...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we were going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop somewhere first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I don't wanna go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!  I don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a good boy, right, Dieter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to give Dieter to anyone until I came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man was his foster parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, he was such a gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could take lessons from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But... that man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that child...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He insisted on going with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hartmann's study...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seasons are all different, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...these were all taken at the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this guy with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All these pictures were taken at Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:11:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From ten years ago, to now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every member of the orphanage, \N including the instructors...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...killed each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that he's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this boy can't see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hartmann!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:13:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This boy can't see... what Johan saw from here back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This boy is not Johan, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The instructors, and even the orphans...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All fifty took their last breath here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just gazed upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gazed upon the spectacle from right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan just gazed upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him just what he had done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he answered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he just threw an oil-soaked rag into a bonfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what he meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hatred is born when people gather together."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I merely poured some oil onto this."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he said!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A boy of only ten years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:14:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made fifty people kill each other without \N lifting one finger of his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is your experiment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.19,0:15:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is your experiment that turned \N him into that kind of person!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our experiment...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is true that Kinderheim 511 was a testing facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A project for turning orphans into perfect soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking back now, that was a \N meager little experiment, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Him, a soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was born to be a leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the one who should have stood at the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way we could have created \N a masterpiece like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:16:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was more than human, a monster, from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made a prediction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end humans just hate and kill each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think Johan's objective was?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be the last person alive at the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is in an abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to be more like Johan because \N of that, even just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you a failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:17:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you be like Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Hartmann!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make another move...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know about Johan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do when \N you know more about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I personally think it is impossible to find and kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you one piece of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, after you hear it, you have to leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find General Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the first to notice Johan's talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's alive somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man in the picture in your study?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man with Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the one who brought Johan in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he knows something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decide on your own whether you want \N to come down from there or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Hartmann puts his finger on the trigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.27,0:18:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decide on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decide with your own free will!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't leave me, can you, Dieter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my child, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that is how it is, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back, my precious little Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can live without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:19:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:19:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is enough, Hartmann!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shoot if you move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is in an abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that tomorrow will be a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to be afraid of!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.76,0:21:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a bus from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and get off at Künen Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.52,0:21:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The orphanage will be right in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give this to a woman named Erna Tiesche.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may look scary on the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she is really a nice old lady at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.03,0:21:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a reason I can't go into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this will be goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.95,0:21:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bus will be here in another two or three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.08,0:21:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practice your soccer skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.47,0:21:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.39,0:21:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.43,0:22:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't come with me...
